<description>
 <p>
   <b>SC4 part number:</b>  </p>
 <p>
   <b>(2) Clause:</b> ARM Express
 </p>
 <p>
   <b>(3) Paragraph:</b> Qualified_property_value_representation, Numerical_item_with_unit, Numerical_representation_context
 </p>
 <p>
   <b>(5) Comment:</b>
 </p>
 <p>
Qualified_property_value_representation refers to Unit through both Numerical_item_with_unit and Numerical_representation_context. Though the two references to units are related, no rule seems to control their correct population.</p>
 <p>
   <b>(6) Proposal:</b>
 </p>
 <p>
Add a rule to Qualified_property_value_representation to control the correct use of Unit.</p>
 </description>
<comment
	by="Nigel Shaw"
	date="04-10-13">
<description>
	The use of Numerical_representation_context is only intended to provide a default unit. Its use is not intended to prevent representation_items being secified with the same or different units to the context. Add a note explaining this. The unit specified with the Numerical_item_with_unit supersedes the unit associated with the context.
</description>
</comment>


<comment
   by="Tom Hendrix"
   date="04-10-31">
<description>
Added note
